parameters.name: KeyPairName
parameters.description: The name of the key pair. The name must be 2 to 128 characters in length. It must start with a letter and cannot start with `http://` or `https://`. It can contain letters, digits, colons (:), underscores (\_), and hyphens (-).

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description: The ID of the region in which to create the key pair. You can call the [DescribeRegions](~~25609~~) operation to query the most recent region list.

parameters.name: ResourceGroupId
parameters.description: The ID of the enterprise resource group to which the SSH key pair belongs.
